1. User sign up service (from user perspective)
1.1 input user email
1.2 output - the user exists (user id) and becoming an active user and a link to user locations


2. Verify user
2.1 Checkin: Mobile App generates bar code with userid and location id 
2.2 The device scans it and send to the server
2.3 Output: user authorized or not

3. Add guest
3.1 Input: user id, location id, name, last name, email, organization
3.2 Output: authorized or not and start and end time.

4 Guest history: based on user id.
